{"id":"20220516cg58522","sourceId":"pr-newswire","sourceName":"PR Newswire","providerName":"PR Newswire","title":"Shareholder Alert: Ademi LLP investigates whether ManTech International Corporation has obtained a Fair Price in its transaction with Carlyle","publishedDate":"2022-05-16T10:15:00-05:00","body":[{"type":"text","content":"Shareholder Alert: Ademi LLP investigates whether ManTech International Corporation has obtained a Fair Price in its transaction with Carlyle\n\n\n\n\n\n","gated":false},{"type":"div","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"h1","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Shareholder Alert: Ademi LLP investigates whether ManTech International Corporation has obtained a Fair Price in its transaction with Carlyle","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"PR Newswire","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"MILWAUKEE, May 16, 2022","gated":false}],"gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n\n","gated":false},{"type":"div","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"MILWAUKEE, May 16, 2022 /PRNewswire/ -- Ademi LLP is investigating ManTech (Nasdaq: MANT) for possible breaches of fiduciary duty and other violations of law in its transaction with Carlyle. ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n\n    ","gated":false},{"type":"div","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n                ","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n                        ","gated":false},{"type":"a","href":"https://mma.prnewswire.com/media/1580107/Ademi_LLP_Logo.html","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n                    ","gated":false},{"type":"img","src":"https://mma.prnewswire.com/media/1580107/Ademi_LLP_Logo.jpg","alt":"AdemiLogo (PRNewsfoto/Ademi LLP)","variations":[],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n                        ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n                ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n\n    ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Click here to learn how to join the action: ","gated":false},{"type":"a","href":"https://www.ademilaw.com/case/mantech-international-corporation","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"https://www.ademilaw.com/case/mantech-international-corporation","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" or call Guri Ademi toll-free at 866-264-3995.  There is no cost or obligation to you.","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Ademi LLP alleges ManTech's financial outlook and prospects are excellent and yet ManTech holders will receive only $96.00 per share in an all-cash transaction with a total enterprise value of approximately $4.2 billion. The transaction agreement unreasonably limits competing bids for ManTech by prohibiting solicitation of further bids, and imposing a significant penalty if ManTech accepts a superior bid. ManTech insiders will receive substantial benefits as part of change of control arrangements.","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"We are investigating the conduct of ManTech's board of directors, and whether they are (i) fulfilling their fiduciary duties to all shareholders, and (ii) obtaining a fair and reasonable price for ManTech.","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"If you own ManTech common stock and wish to obtain additional information, ple